## Erlang VM configuration for Arbor releases

## Pin distribution port range for firewalls
## EPMD uses 4369, distribution uses this range
-kernel inet_dist_listen_min 9100
-kernel inet_dist_listen_max 9155

## Increase net_ticktime to 120s (disconnect after ~8 min of no response)
## Tolerates brief network hiccups, sleep/wake, and idle periods
-kernel net_ticktime 120
